	<p><em><strong>SW</strong> replies:</em> Yup, can't be arsed is dead right. I can't be arsed, for a load of (IMO) very good reasons; not least amongst them is that I am vehemently opposed to the idea that we need a centralised government at all.</p>
	<small>
